sequenceDiagram
    participant U as User
    participant F as Frontend
    participant B as Backend
    participant DB as Database
    participant E as Email Service

    U->>F: Register (email, login, password)
    F->>B: POST /auth/register
    B->>DB: Create user (unverified)
    B->>E: Send verification code
    B-->>F: Success message
    F-->>U: Check email

    U->>F: Verify email (code)
    F->>B: POST /auth/verify-email
    B->>DB: Mark email verified
    B-->>F: Success
    F-->>U: Can login now

    U->>F: Login (login/email, password)
    F->>B: POST /auth/login
    B->>DB: Validate credentials
    B-->>F: access_token, refresh_token
    F-->>U: Logged in

    Note over F: Tokens stored in localStorage/cookies

    U->>F: Access protected route
    F->>B: Request with Bearer token
    B->>B: Validate JWT
    B-->>F: Data or 401